{"tid":1674943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(預言) 想講下陸永首【問題兒童】","createTime":"2019-10-25T13:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T14:49:18.000Z","uid":102775,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33878b7b2be7dbd4fd1ba65b3f723d621b79d7b3","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"呢首歌雖然係9年前發行嘅，但係依然聽到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前半段基本上都係講緊好多發達社會一路有嘅問題，所以就唔係到詳細講啦，自己click入去聽下啦。<br />\n<br />\n至於後半段嘅歌詞就算而家聽返，感覺9年前已經為咗而家嘅香港人作呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>點解大話係大人嘅共通語言 細路講大話大人又有怨言</ins></span><br />\n721 821 101 yellow object 陳彥霖事件等等，班黑警不斷大話冚大話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>邊個發明子彈當人係紙板 <br />\n國家攻打國家 係咪正義嘅示範</ins></span><br />\n612 811 101外加無數粒子彈 催淚彈 槍槍都當打香港人紙板咁打<br />\n港共嚴重打壓香港人人權 完全係獨裁不義嘅示範<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>佢地話平等 土地係咪平分 邊個發明地產 我分到塊地板</ins></span><br />\n嚴重嘅住屋問題香港一路有 唔係比晒每日150個蝗就係係晒地產商到 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>邊個發明鎖鏈鎖住所謂嘅罪人</ins></span><br />\n自六月起黑警不斷濫捕加濫用私刑 而被拉嘅義士更加只係為咗爭取我哋應有嘅民主自由<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>係咪我太過古怪 問題問得太Kai 點解人一大就習慣晒呢個世界</ins></span><br />\n差唔多最後提醒我哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好習慣</span></strong>，好好警惕住上面問過嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來陸永唔止個樣似天琦 連歌詞都行前咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWg2ihamQqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCWg2ihamQqQ&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=eb5affde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWg2ihamQqQ</a>"},{"pid":"9140a0f10c626af7186d6d6fbe77aab14fd69cb6","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"60747b94b65024cddb80ff789867f87f808ddf93","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"517a71b51a3613db7587150da1d536c29ab9cc8e","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRtty2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRtty2t.jpg&h=55d5041d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWgKRO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWgKRO8.jpg&h=92bae644&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWnibO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWnibO8.jpg&h=f3a8e8e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n千祈唔好慣啊"},{"pid":"89eb9aa1aef2cd5a04cd7dba3abc034c94027d36","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f2c663c4b258e0ef822478e26e22a18be0b6f8e","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d442332b1fe536a6d46f94c18cc615078708c4a","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7749ef9cdb8b728abfdd3078e77a656cd45541f","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4fed529acedc7c50e4f8d7d43def23b75dd9c9a","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"159b83695d22196d91c59c9d898081303b1bc1a5","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35dcef021c3f83c8902b6b4630f66e4456c0c7ec","tid":1674943,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci